*Tomi* je u školi bio najbolji učenik (Tomi was the best student in school).
U *Tomi*noj obitelji svi su bili vrijedni (Everybody in Tomi's family was hardworking).
*Tomi* je uvijek znao što bi trebao napraviti (Tomi always knew what he should do).
*Tomiju* je bio potreban odmor (Tomi needed a rest).
*Tomija* su svi voljeli (Everybody loved Tomi).